.body
  p Hi #{name},

  p Welcome to Flipping the Scales. Before you go any further, we need to make sure you are a real person.  Please click the button below to confirm your email address.

  a.button(href=`${serverURL}userVerification/${userID}/${verificationString}?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=VerifyEmail`) Confirm Email
