    | Also, to get you up and running as quickly as possible - I have created a short 
    a(href='https://www.flippingthescales.com/blog/flipping-the-scales-competition-setup/?utm_source=email&utm_campaign=VerifyEmail') guide
    |  that explains how to create your first competition.  I hope you'll find it helpful.
  p Best,
  p Ryan